column5: Yeah def going smaller when healed thank you
CONGRATULATIONS!! FUCK YEAH YOU ROCK!! So proud of you!!
I’m in between jobs now actually because I can’t seem to hold one down for long.
Way to go!!! Really proud of you!
I’m smoking a pack a day and I don’t smoke. I’m easy to anger which is unusual for me. I’m very distrustful of other people and I’m talking a lot more where I’m normally reserved.
